#. Tag: title
#: man-ark.1.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "वर्णनम्‌"

#. Tag: para
#: man-ark.1.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&ark; is a program for managing various compressed file formats within "
"&kde;. Archives can be viewed, extracted, created and modified with &ark;. "
"The program can handle various formats such as <application>tar</"
"application>, <application>gzip</application>, <application>bzip2</"
"application>, <application>zip</application>, <application>rar</application> "
"(when the appropriate libraries or command-line programs are installed)."
msgstr ""
"&ark; &kde;-अन्तर्गतं विविधसंपीडितसञ्चिकास्वरूपाणां प्रबन्धनार्थं कार्यक्रमः अस्ति । "
"अभिलेखागारं &ark; इत्यनेन द्रष्टुं, निष्कासयितुं, निर्मातुं, परिवर्तनं च कर्तुं शक्यते । कार्यक्रमः "
"<application>tar</application>, <application>gzip</application>, "
"<application>bzip2</application>, <application>zip</application>, "
"<application>rar</ इत्यादीनि विविधानि प्रारूपाणि सम्भालितुं शक्नोति । application> "
"(यदा समुचितपुस्तकालयाः अथवा आदेशपङ्क्तिकार्यक्रमाः संस्थापिताः भवन्ति)।"

#. Tag: title
#: man-ark.1.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "Operation modes"
msgstr "संचालनविधानानि"

#. Tag: para
#: man-ark.1.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&ark; can be used either as a stand-alone &GUI; program as well as a command-"
"line program in order to perform some specific tasks."
msgstr ""
"&ark; एकान्तरूपेण वा उपयोक्तुं शक्यते &GUI; program अपि च केचन विशिष्टानि कार्याणि कर्तुं "
"आदेशपङ्क्तिकार्यक्रमः ।"

#. Tag: para
#: man-ark.1.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If invoked without the -b (--batch) or -c (--add) options, &ark; is started "
"as a normal &GUI; program."
msgstr ""
"यदि -b (--batch) अथवा -c (--add) विकल्पान् विना आह्वयते तर्हि &ark; सामान्यरूपेण "
"आरभ्यते &GUI; कार्यक्रम।"

#. Tag: para
#: man-ark.1.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When the -b (--batch) option is used, &ark; can be used to extract the "
"contents of one or more files directly from the command-line, without "
"launching its &GUI;."
msgstr ""
"यदा -b (--batch) विकल्पः प्रयुक्तः भवति तदा &ark; एकस्य वा अधिकस्य सञ्चिकायाः "
"सामग्रीं प्रत्यक्षतया आदेशपङ्क्तौ निष्कासयितुं उपयोक्तुं शक्यते, तस्य &GUI;."

#. Tag: para
#: man-ark.1.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When the -c (--add) option is used, &ark; prompts for files that should be "
"added to a new archive or to an existing archive."
msgstr ""
"यदा -c (--add) विकल्पः प्रयुक्तः भवति तदा &ark; नूतनसङ्ग्रहे विद्यमानसङ्ग्रहे वा "
"योजितव्याः सञ्चिकाः प्रार्थयति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: man-ark.1.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options"
msgstr "विकल्पाः"

#. Tag: option
#: man-ark.1.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid "-d, --dialog"
msgstr "-द, --संवादः"

#. Tag: para
#: man-ark.1.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show a dialog for specifying the options for a batch or add operation."
msgstr "बैच् अथवा add ऑपरेशन इत्यस्य विकल्पान् निर्दिष्टुं संवादं दर्शयतु ।"

#. Tag: option
#: man-ark.1.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "-m, --mimetypes"
msgstr "-म, --मिमप्रकाराः"

#. Tag: para
#: man-ark.1.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid "List supported &MIME; types."
msgstr "सूची समर्थिता &MIME; प्रकाराः ।"

#. Tag: option
#: man-ark.1.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid "-o, --destination <replaceable>directory</replaceable>"
msgstr "-ओ, --गन्तव्य <प्रतिस्थापनीय>निर्देशिका</प्रतिस्थापनीय>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-ark.1.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Default the extraction directory to <replaceable>directory</replaceable>. If "
"not passed, the current path is used."
msgstr ""
"निष्कर्षणनिर्देशिकां पूर्वनिर्धारितरूपेण <replaceable>directory</replaceable> इति "
"स्थापयन्तु । यदि न उत्तीर्णः तर्हि वर्तमानमार्गः उपयुज्यते ।"

#. Tag: title
#: man-ark.1.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options for adding files"
msgstr "सञ्चिकाः योजयितुं विकल्पाः"

#. Tag: option
#: man-ark.1.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid "-c, --add"
msgstr "-ग, --जोड़"

#. Tag: para
#: man-ark.1.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Query the user for an archive filename and add specified files to it. Quit "
"when finished."
msgstr ""
"उपयोक्तारं संग्रहसञ्चिकानामार्थं पृच्छन्तु तस्मिन् निर्दिष्टसञ्चिकाः योजयन्तु । समाप्ते सति त्यजतु।"

#. Tag: option
#: man-ark.1.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid "-t, --add-to <replaceable>filename</replaceable>"
msgstr "-t, --add-to <replaceable>सञ्चिकानाम</replaceable> इति"

#. Tag: para
#: man-ark.1.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Add the specified files to <replaceable>filename</replaceable>. Create "
"archive if it does not exist. Quit when finished."
msgstr ""
"निर्दिष्टसञ्चिकाः <replaceable>filename</replaceable> इत्यत्र योजयन्तु । यदि संग्रहणं "
"नास्ति तर्हि संग्रहणं रचयन्तु। समाप्ते सति त्यजतु।"

#. Tag: option
#: man-ark.1.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid "-p, --changetofirstpath"
msgstr "-प, --प्रथममार्गे परिवर्तन"

#. Tag: para
#: man-ark.1.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Change the current directory to the first entry and add all other entries "
"relative to this one."
msgstr ""
"वर्तमाननिर्देशिकां प्रथमप्रविष्टौ परिवर्त्य अस्य सापेक्षतया अन्याः सर्वाः प्रविष्टयः योजयन्तु ।"

#. Tag: option
#: man-ark.1.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid "-f, --autofilename <replaceable>suffix</replaceable>"
msgstr "-f, --autofilename <प्रतिस्थापनीय>प्रत्यय</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-ark.1.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Automatically choose a filename, with the selected <replaceable>suffix</"
"replaceable> (for example rar, tar.gz, zip or any other supported types)."
msgstr ""
"स्वयमेव सञ्चिकानाम चिनोतु, चयनितेन <replaceable>प्रत्ययेन</replaceable> (उदाहरणार्थं "
"rar, tar.gz, zip अथवा अन्ये समर्थिताः प्रकाराः) ।"

#. Tag: title
#: man-ark.1.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options for batch extraction"
msgstr "बैच-निष्कासनस्य विकल्पाः"

#. Tag: option
#: man-ark.1.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid "-b, --batch"
msgstr "-ख, --बैच"

#. Tag: para
#: man-ark.1.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the batch interface instead of the usual dialog. This option is implied "
"if more than one url is specified."
msgstr ""
"सामान्यसंवादस्य स्थाने batch interface इत्यस्य उपयोगं कुर्वन्तु । यदि एकादशाधिकं url "
"निर्दिष्टं भवति तर्हि एषः विकल्पः अभिप्रेतः ।"

#. Tag: option
#: man-ark.1.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid "-e, --autodestination"
msgstr "-ई, --स्वयं गन्तव्य"

#. Tag: para
#: man-ark.1.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The destination argument will be set to the path of the first file supplied."
msgstr "गन्तव्यतर्कं प्रथमसञ्चिकायाः मार्गे सेट् भविष्यति ।"

#. Tag: option
#: man-ark.1.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid "-a, --autosubfolder"
msgstr "-क, --स्वतः उपपुटम्"

#. Tag: para
#: man-ark.1.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Archive contents will be read, and if detected to not be a single folder "
"archive, a subfolder by the name of the archive will be created."
msgstr ""
"संग्रहसामग्री पठिता भविष्यति, यदि एकः पुटसङ्ग्रहः नास्ति इति ज्ञायते तर्हि संग्रहस्य नाम "
"उपपुटं निर्मितं भविष्यति ।"

#. Tag: option
#: man-ark.1.docbook:174
#, no-c-format
msgid "-O, --opendestination"
msgstr "-हे, --मुक्तगतिः"

#. Tag: para
#: man-ark.1.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open the destination folder when the extraction is complete."
msgstr "यदा निष्कर्षणं समाप्तं भवति तदा गन्तव्यपुटं उद्घाटयन्तु ।"

#. Tag: title
#: man-ark.1.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid "See Also"
msgstr "इदमपि पश्यन्तु"

#. Tag: member
#: man-ark.1.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"More detailed user documentation is available from <ulink url=\"help:/ark"
"\">help:/ark</ulink> (either enter this &URL; into &konqueror;, or run "
"<userinput><command>khelpcenter</command> <parameter>help:/ark</parameter></"
"userinput>)."
msgstr ""
"अधिकविस्तृतं उपयोक्तृदस्तावेजं <ulink url=\"help:/ark\">help:/ark</ulink> इत्यस्मात् "
"उपलभ्यते (एतत् &URL; &konqueror; मध्ये प्रविशतु, अथवा "
"<userinput><command>khelpcenter</command> < चालयन्तु पैरामीटर>सहायता:/ark</"
"parameter></userinput>)।"

#. Tag: member
#: man-ark.1.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid "kf6options(7)"
msgstr "kf6विकल्पाः(7) ."

#. Tag: member
#: man-ark.1.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid "qt6options(7)"
msgstr "qt6विकल्प(7) 1.1."

#. Tag: title
#: man-ark.1.docbook:198
#, no-c-format
msgid "Examples"
msgstr "उदाहरणानि"

#. Tag: userinput
#: man-ark.1.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>ark</command> <option>--batch</option> <replaceable>archive.tar."
"bz2</replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<command>आर्क</command><option value=--batch> --राशिः</option><replaceable> "
"संग्रह.तर.bz2</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-ark.1.docbook:205
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Will extract <replaceable>archive.tar.bz2</replaceable> into the current "
"directory without showing any &GUI;."
msgstr ""
"<replaceable>archive.tar.bz2</replaceable> इत्येतत् वर्तमाननिर्देशिकायां किमपि &GUI;"
"प्रदर्शनं विना निष्कासयिष्यति ।"

#. Tag: userinput
#: man-ark.1.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>ark</command> <option>-b</option> <option>-d</option> "
"<replaceable>archive.tar.bz2</replaceable> <replaceable>archive2.zip</"
"replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<command>आर्क</command><option value=-b> -ख</option><option value=-d> -घ</"
"option><replaceable> संग्रह.तर.bz2</replaceable><replaceable> आर्काइव२.जिप्</"
"replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-ark.1.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Will first show an extraction options dialog and then extract both "
"<replaceable>archive.tar.bz2</replaceable> and <replaceable>archive2.zip</"
"replaceable> into the directory chosen in the dialog."
msgstr ""
"प्रथमं निष्कर्षणविकल्पसंवादं दर्शयिष्यति ततः संवादे चयनितनिर्देशिकायां "
"<replaceable>archive.tar.bz2</replaceable> तथा <replaceable>archive2.zip</"
"replaceable> इत्येतयोः द्वयोः अपि निष्कासनं करिष्यति"

#. Tag: userinput
#: man-ark.1.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>ark</command> <option>--add-to</option> <replaceable>my-archive."
"zip</replaceable> <replaceable>photo1.jpg</replaceable> <replaceable>text."
"txt</replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<command>आर्क</command><option value=--add-to> --जोड-त इति</"
"option><replaceable> my-archive.zip इति</replaceable><replaceable> photo1."
"jpg इति</replaceable><replaceable> पाठ.txt</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-ark.1.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Will create <replaceable>my-archive.zip</replaceable> if does not exist and "
"then add <replaceable>photo1.jpg</replaceable> and <replaceable>text.txt</"
"replaceable> to it."
msgstr ""
"यदि नास्ति तर्हि <replaceable>my-archive.zip</replaceable> निर्मास्यति ततः तस्मिन् "
"<replaceable>photo1.jpg</replaceable> तथा <replaceable>text.txt</"
"replaceable> योजयिष्यति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: man-ark.1.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid "Maintainership"
msgstr "परिपालनम्"

#. Tag: para
#: man-ark.1.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&ark; is currently maintained by <emphasis role=\"bold\">Elvis Angelaccio</"
"emphasis> and <emphasis role=\"bold\">Ragnar Thomsen</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"&ark; सम्प्रति <emphasis role=\"bold\">एल्विस् एन्जेलाक्सिओ</emphasis> तथा "
"<emphasis role=\"bold\">राग्नर थोम्सेन्</emphasis> इत्यनेन परिपालितम् अस्ति ।"
